OL,6,F"Between Rhosili and the Mumbles area,
OL,7,Fit's either fourteen or seventeen
OL,8,Fmiles of cliff, and I think there's
OL,9,Fonly three farmers grazing it now.
OL,10,FThere would have been hundreds."
OL,12,FMr Beynon has also had to move his
OL,13,Fhorses to other pastures due to past
OL,14,Fattacks.
OL,16,FHe added: "Everyone's answer to the
OL,17,Fproblems are signs- put more signs up-
OL,18,F people don't read signs anymore,
OL,19,Fthey're too busy looking at their
OL,20,Fphone screens.
