OL,6,F"Then all of a sudden, the dog is
OL,7,Fgone."
OL,9,FThe value of Welsh farm animals killed
OL,10,For seriously injured in attacks has
OL,11,Fmore than doubled, according to new
OL,12,Fdata from NFU Mutual.
OL,14,FIt reached an estimated #883,000 in
OL,15,F2023, more than double the #439,000
OL,16,Ffigure reported in 2022.
