OL,4,Cattacks says 'enough is enough'
OL,6,FThe figures also revealed an increase
OL,7,Fin the number of dog owners allowing
OL,8,Ftheir pets to roam off leads in the
OL,9,Fcountryside. 68% of surveyed dog
OL,10,Fowners admitted to this practice, yet
OL,11,Fless than half (49%) are able to
OL,12,Freliably recall their dogs when
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,FNFU Mutual is issuing a heartfelt plea
OL,16,Ffor responsible dog ownership to
OL,17,Fmitigate the risk of future
OL,18,Fdevastating attacks.
