OL,6,FMore livestock attacks have also seen
OL,7,Fmore calls made to rural mental health
OL,8,Fcharities.
OL,10,FKate Miles, manager of the DPJ
OL,11,FFoundation, told ITV Wales: "At this
OL,12,Ftime of year we're hearing of sheep
OL,13,Fthat are losing lambs as a result of
OL,14,Fhaving been chased and then going into
OL,15,Fpremature labour.
OL,17,F"We're also hearing cases of cattle
OL,18,Fbeing chased and the effect on them."
