OL,6,FRural insurer, NFU Mutual, is also
OL,7,Fthrowing its support behind a new
OL,8,Fparliamentary Bill designed to enhance
OL,9,Fthe powers available to police for
OL,10,Fdealing with dog attacks on livestock.
OL,12,FThis legislative initiative aims to
OL,13,Fprovide law enforcement with the
OL,14,Fnecessary tools to address this
OL,15,Fgrowing threat effectively.
OL,17,FAcross the UK as a whole, dog attacks
OL,18,Fon livestock were estimated to cost
OL,19,F#2.4 million last year, up nearly 30%
OL,20,Fcompared to the previous year
