OL,6,FThis comes as the Dogs (Protection of
OL,7,FLivestock) (Amendment) Bill is making
OL,8,Fits way through parliament.
OL,10,FNFU Mutual Wales manager, Owen
OL,11,FSuckley, called these figures
OL,12,F"shocking" and "alarming" due to the
OL,13,Fincoming 2024 lambing season which
OL,14,Fwill see many fields populated with
OL,15,Fvulnerable ewes and newborn lambs.
