OL,4,Cattacks says 'enough is enough'
OL,6,FHe added: "We've heard reports from
OL,7,Ffarmers about the complacency and
OL,8,Fnaivety of some dog owners who
OL,9,Fregularly allow their pets to roam off-
OL,10,Flead in the countryside, seemingly
OL,11,Funaware of the carnage the dog could
OL,12,Fcause, then are horrified when an
OL,13,Fattack happens.
OL,15,F"There have also been incidences where
OL,16,Fdogs have chased, injured and killed
OL,17,Fsheep and the owner is nowhere to be
OL,18,Fseen."
